720112f-b.title: Manhattan: Grand Street - Attorney Street
720112f-b.text:
(1)
Grand Street, north side, east from but not including Attorney,
to and including Pitt Streets. Also shown is St. Mary's Roman
Catholic Church, at the N.W. corner of Ridge Street.
April 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, from a different angle.
NE6 ~ 267~  July 22, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
